text: Knockanure is a village in County Kerry, Ireland, and is located near the town of Listowel and the village of Moyvane. == Amenities == Knockanure has one church, The Church Of Corpus Christi, which was built in 1964. Scoil Chorp Chríost is the primary school in Knockanure. The pub is called Flynn's Bar. == Notable residents == * Dan Keane (1919–2012), poet == References == Category:Towns and villages in County Kerry
